ternary totalistic elementary cellular automata

ternary = 3 possible states
totalistic = ruleset looks at sum of neighbourhood
elemetnary = 1 dimensional array
min sum = 0, max sum = 6, 7 total possibilities
3 to the power of 7 = 2187
All 2187 rulesets statically rendered at built time
